flowchart LR
    DEV[Developer]
    USER[User Browser]

    DEV -->|Code / Commit / Push| GH[GitHub Repository]

    subgraph GHA[GitHub Actions]
        CI[CI Pipeline<br/>Frontend Build<br/>Backend Validation / Test]
        CD[CD Pipeline<br/>SSH Deploy to EC2]
    end

    GH -->|Push / PR| CI
    GH -->|Push to main| CD
    GH -->|Git Integration| VERCEL[Vercel<br/>React SPA Hosting]

    CD -->|SSH :22| EC2HOST[EC2 Ubuntu Server]

    subgraph EC2BOX[EC2 Runtime]
        DEPLOY[deploy.sh<br/>git fetch / reset --hard<br/>docker build<br/>docker rm<br/>docker run]
        NGINX[Nginx Reverse Proxy<br/>:80 Redirect / :443 HTTPS<br/>SSL Termination]

        subgraph DOCKER[Docker Runtime]
            APP[Django + Gunicorn Container<br/>:8000]
        end
    end

    EC2HOST --> DEPLOY
    DEPLOY --> APP

    USER -->|Open Web App<br/>HTTPS :443| VERCEL
    VERCEL --> FE[React SPA]

    subgraph FRONT[Frontend Runtime]
        STATE[Context API / Reducer<br/>Auth / Cart / Filters]
        AXIOS[Axios Instance<br/>withCredentials: true<br/>401 → refresh → retry]
        ROUTER[React Router]
    end

    FE --> ROUTER
    FE --> STATE
    FE --> AXIOS

    AXIOS -->|HTTPS API Request :443| DOMAIN[purepro-api.duckdns.org]
    DOMAIN --> NGINX
    NGINX -->|proxy_pass<br/>127.0.0.1:8000| APP

    subgraph BACK[Backend Runtime]
        AUTH[JWT Authentication<br/>HttpOnly Cookies<br/>access / refresh]
        API[Domain APIs<br/>/api/auth/*<br/>/api/products/*<br/>/api/address/*<br/>/api/orders/*<br/>/api/reviews/*<br/>/api/profile/*]
        ORM[Django ORM]
    end

    APP --> AUTH
    APP --> API
    APP --> ORM

    ORM --> RDS[(Amazon RDS PostgreSQL<br/>:5432)]
    APP --> REDIS[(Redis / Valkey<br/>:6379 optional)]
    APP --> S3[(Amazon S3<br/>Media Storage<br/>HTTPS :443)]

    APP -->|Set-Cookie in Response| USER
    USER -->|Auto-send Cookies| AXIOS

    GH -.contains.-> DOCKERFILE[Dockerfile<br/>Backend Container Definition]
    DOCKERFILE -.used by.-> DEPLOY